# CVE-2023-44487 (HTTP/2 Rapid Reset Attack)
# Justification: Our ALB terminates HTTP/2 before it reaches this container.
# This service only accepts internal traffic from the ALB target group.
# Fix available in a newer alpine version but causes dependency conflicts.
# Risk accepted by: Ahtesham Shah (22F-3627)
